L\left(\frac{1}{\theta}\right)^{\frac{1}{1-\theta}}p_{h}^{\frac{2-\theta}{1-\theta}}-L\left(\frac{p_{h}}{\theta}\right)^{\frac{1}{1-\theta}}\sigma-S
